Landing page:
- Two tabs
	* Host a Split or Join a Split

Host page:
- Generates a code
	* Four uppercase letters
- Instructions on how to join the Split

Join page:
- Code field
- Submit button

Lobby page:
- Shows host
- Shows joiners
- Shows video and length

Vido page:
- One tap pausese
- Two taps opens overlaying interface (like Youtubes)
- Background has multicolored bars to help users orient devices
